{"tid":134894,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"求屯門天水圍羽毛球波友","createTime":"2017-02-25T23:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T03:50:11.000Z","uid":25196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc42cbf89db761d0787530b9867a8258e1771f94","tid":134894,"uid":25196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T23:40:45.000Z","msg":"星期六or日<br />\n朝早7-9,8-10<br />\n初至初中級<br />\n長打<br />\nTelegram:ITisDog"},{"pid":"768173514235045bae9ca01f9ebf05e0eb54b413","tid":134894,"uid":72477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T23:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期六or日<br />\n朝早7-9,8-10<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">初至初中級</span><br />\n長打<br />\nTelegram:ITisDog</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無高中級同大專級？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ce28bdc4bf862fe5dea4e9fd56977f40c44232","tid":134894,"uid":18923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>星期六or日<br />\n朝早7-9,8-10<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">初至初中級</span><br />\n長打<br />\nTelegram:ITisDog</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無高中級同大專級？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n必須按程度參加:<br />\n<br />\n快樂級 :<br />\n初接觸羽毛球, 不熟球例, 只求出一身汗.<br />\n<br />\n初級 :<br />\n熟知雙打球例(新制21分), 懂正/反手開波, 肯走肯追波, 正手回球到中場, 唔怕比人打死.<br />\n<br />\n初至初中級:<br />\n已非常習慣打game, 開波唔叉燒, 能應付貼近底線的球, 開始能控制球的方向, 識放下網, 殺下波, 回球偶爾餵叉燒.<br />\n<br />\n初中級 :<br />\n已有連續打球2年經驗, 曾跟教練學習基本技術最少半年. 能輕易打出高遠底線到底線, drop波/平推/放網樣樣識啲, 後場都要殺到波, 可以多球來回, 必須懂雙打走位.<br />\n<br />\n初中至中級 :<br />\n&quot;殺吊擘滑推拉搓&quot;全部掌握, 反手輕易後場至後場, 雙打走位唔少得, 久唔久仲有幾下trick shot, 攻守兼備.<br />\n<br />\n中級 :<br />\n有公開比賽經驗, 反手殺波, 有細膩假動作, 步法比球快到點, 打位控制對手."},{"pid":"2975d37d9fb4638bde5e222308572fbe994abee6","tid":134894,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:56:36.000Z","msg":"打公開賽都過級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7433fdd5b7193e04405ed5e75beaf377e2c6c130","tid":134894,"uid":25196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:23:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"82a8aa53a655ca524262541915be54bcfc96d1fa","tid":134894,"uid":25196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"561792b57911c2c5e6bcf250adcb0e10710b023c","tid":134894,"uid":25196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"16016fba0bc62fd0b8b101f286cacc3c11a5ff52","tid":134894,"uid":25196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"日期：3月12日(星期日)<br />\n地點：屯門良田體育館<br />\n時間：7-9 am (1+1)<br />\n級別：初至初中級雙打（新手/初學/撲蝶者不宜）<br />\n用球：RSL No.1<br />\n費用：每位$45 視乎人數及用球數微調<br />\n名額：Max 6 (-2)"},{"pid":"65c7a327df4a6f9f5972cad1589cc82f25675b5b","tid":134894,"uid":25196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:50:11.000Z","msg":"日期：3月12日(星期日)<br />\n地點：屯門良田體育館<br />\n時間：7-9 am (1+1)<br />\n級別：初至初中級雙打（新手/初學/撲蝶者不宜）<br />\n用球：RSL No.1<br />\n費用：每位$45 視乎人數及用球數微調<br />\n名額：Max 6 (-1）"}]}